itemListElement.name: The Owl 'N Thistle Irish Pub and Restaurant

name: The Owl 'N Thistle Irish Pub and Restaurant
Mecca Cafe
description: One of Seattle's oldest diners with a legendary dive bar. Stiff drinks and huge portions of homemade diner classics. Open for breakfast, lunch, dinner and late night. Seattle's best happy hour. We're known for our great Philly Cheesesteaks, hamburgers, chicken fried steak, sandwiches, fish & chips and Pot Roast. And we're famous for our small, dimly lit dive bar. We've been serving Queen Anne since 1930. In the shadow of the Space Needle and steps away from Seattle Center and the new Climate Pledge Arena. A great place to eat and drink before and after Kraken games!
